@NumberOne CakeDiva. If you look at the reviews from new residents you’ll notice they are enjoying the new improvements from new ownership since October 2017.

I don’t understand how you came to your conclusion and it’s unfair to folks looking for a clean and safe community that cares about its residents and is renovating the park.

Were you recently evicted? Have you been inside a remodeled home? If you were to tour interiors you would see where all our labor and materials have been going. The Park renovations began in October 2017 and we are 70% done, but Interiors were completed first. The Exterior renovations to wrap up the project and provide the curb appeal you’re looking for will be completed by October 2018. I hope that helps. Let me know if you have any other questions.
